										class Attribute2
										{
											property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Description";
											expression="_this setVariable ['Description',_value,true];";
											class Value
											{
												class data
												{
													singleType="STRING";
													value="<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>=== SITUATION ===</font>        " \n "<br/><br/>      " \n "At the border of Lithuania, The Russians have started conducting aggressive military exercises close to the border. Coincidentally, a surge of militia cells has started popping up all around the country. Ruha having the highest amount of activity.  " \n "<br/><br/>    " \n "Lithuanian intel suggests, this group is backed by the Russians to cause mayhem and chaos whilst asking to be free from the current government, The US has responded to the situation by conducting its own military exercise alongside the Lithuanians as a show of force to deter any possible Russian aggression.  " \n "<br/><br/>    " \n "High Command  has deployed  the 1st Special Operations Group alongside the 3rd Special Forces Group and the 160th soar into Ruha with hopes of eliminating the increasing insurgent threat." \n "<br/><br/> " \n "<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>=== Mission ===</font>  " \n "<br/><br/>  " \n "The insurgents have a semblence of a command structure, taking the heads out of the picture might stomp these guys for good." \n "<br/><br/>" \n "There's at least 2 Militia Officers in play. Taking them alive would be crucial since, they might be able to give more info on other cells in the region. " \n "<br/><br/>" \n "They also have a bunch of ammo and equipement caches laying around, Find and Destroy them." \n "<br/><br/>" \n "That's all Good hunting gents.";
												};
											};
										};
